yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Mahmoud has suffered a terrible injury and loss.
yingyinNormal.zh: 默罕默德先生遭受了巨大的伤害和损失。

yingyinNormal.en: The electrical injury may have caused intra-abdominal tissue damage and likely progressing because of his heart failing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电击伤害可能造成了腹内组织损伤，由于心脏骤停，可能已经恶化了。

yingyinNormal.en: This kind of experience happens to everyone. It will happen to you. You will lose something, or someone you think you can't live without. Or you will suffer a terrible illness or injury, or your career will fall apart before your eyes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有人能幸免这种事。它会发生在你身上。你会失去一切失去不能失去的人。或者会遭受严重的疾病或伤害，或者眼见着自己的职业生涯分崩离析。

yingyinNormal.en: I cannot walk into that E.R. with another video game injury.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没脸再因为打游戏受伤而走进急诊室了。

yingyinNormal.en: I will scan you for injury. Don't scan me. Scan complete. Unbelievable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我为你扫描，看是否受伤。别扫我。扫描完毕。不可理喻。

yingyinNormal.en: What? Blood. Quite a bit of it, too. Was there any injury at the crime scene? Nah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了？血。而且还不少。犯罪现场有人受伤吗？没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Still hurts. I seen no evidence of physical injury. It's a different kind of hurt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但还是很痛。我没有检测出伤口。那是另外一种伤痛。

yingyinNormal.en: We have to fill these out. Describe illness or injury. I dislocated my shoulder. All right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们得先填表格。请描述病情和伤情情况。肩膀脱臼。好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: To see if he's getting better? No, it's a spinal-cord injury. He's not going to get better.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看有没有好转吗？不，他是脊髓损伤，不可能好转。

yingyinNormal.en: Good idea. I need my wrist brace. All this button-pushing is aggravating my old Nintendo injury.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好主意，我得活动下腕关节，按这些键弄得我以前玩任天堂留下的老伤更严重了。

yingyinNormal.en: I've had a recent head injury and certain numbers and days. Barbecue. Oh, did l? See, there you go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最近头部受伤，只记得一些数字了，野外烤肉，哦，我应该去吗？好的。

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't say that. Ms. Searle's injury is unfortunate, but it has nothing whatever to do with my car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有这么说，瑟尔女士受伤是很不幸，可是她受伤和我的车没关系。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's that? That's my neighbor, Bailey. He was brought in with a head injury. I know you're talking about me, Destiny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是谁？是我邻居，利鲸。他被送进来时头受伤。我知道你在说我，命运。

yingyinNormal.en: And it means giving our wounded warriors all the care and support they need to heal including mental health care for those with post-traumatic stress or traumatic brain injury.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这意味着给予我们的伤残军人所有他们在痊愈中所需的照料和帮助包括对那些有着创伤后压力或者创伤性脑损伤军人的心理健康护理。
